NG0505:3: thams cad rang rig byang chub nyid //
NG0505:4: rang nyid bcings na kun yang bcings //
NG0505:5: rang dang gzhan nyid gcig pa'i phyir //
NG0505:6: gzhan nyid bcings na rang yang bcings //
NG0505:7: gzhan dang rang nyid gcig pa'i phyir //
NG0505:8: gcig la 'char lugs tha dad pa //
NG0505:9: sgo lnga dbang po so sor gsal //
NG0505:10: der byung snang ba sna tshogs te //
NG0505:11: don ni sems la 'das pa med //
NG0505:12: yal 'dab mang yang sdong po'i ngos //
NG0505:13: gzhan du 'gyur ba med bzhin du //
NG0505:14: bdag gzhan don gnyis 'grub pa'i sa //
NG0505:15: byang chub sems kyi 'bras bu de //
NG0505:16: bdag nyid mngon par sangs rgyas tshe //
NG0505:18: sangs rgyas gnyis snang rtogs can 'gyur //
NG0505:19: sems can 'khrul snang ma mchis na //
NG0505:20: thams cad mkhyen pa'i dgos pa stor //
NG0505:21: rang la sku gnyis snang gyur ni //
NG0505:22: gnyis med chos sku don la bsgribs //
NG0505:23: chos skus kun la ma khyab na //
NG0505:24: sangs rgyas yon tan ma mchis te //
NG0505:25: ye shes med na nyon mongs dngos //
NG0505:26: bag la nyal ba yod ma srid //
NG0505:27: yod na de'i rgyu mtshan shod //
NG0505:28: byang chub sems kyi gnas lugs ni //
NG0505:29: thog med dus nas ma rig pas //
NG0505:30: nyon mongs rang gsal sna tshogs 'di //
NG0505:31: 'khor ba kun rdzob bden par shar //
NG0505:32: rang gis gnyen por rang nyid kyi //
NG0505:33: lta sgom spyod pa'i sems bskyed kyi //
NG0505:34: 'khor ba rang snang sems su rtogs //
NG0505:35: rjes shes rmi lam sgyu ma tsam //
NG0505:36: mnyam par bzhag pa 'od gsal dang *//
NG0505:37: byang chub sems dpa' mnyam rjes la //
NG0505:39: nam yin langs pa'i mun pa 'dra //
NG0505:40: mnyam rjes med pa chos kyi sku //
NG0505:42: bu tsa'i dus kyi snang ba de //
NG0505:43: che mir gyur nas med gyur kyang *//
NG0505:44: bu tsa'i byed spyod mtshan nyid shes //
NG0505:45: shes kyang bu tsar mi ldog bzhin //
NG0505:46: sangs rgyas 'khor bar mi snang yang *//
NG0505:47: 'khor ba'i dus kyi mtshan nyid shes //
NG0505:48: shes kyang shes bya'i sgrib pa med //
NG0505:49: sangs rgyas 'khor bar mi ldog ste //
NG0505:51: sangs rgyas min pa'i sems can med //
NG0505:52: sems can thams cad sangs rgyas pas //
NG0505:53: gnyis med chos sku khyab brdal la //
NG0505:54: nyon mongs rang bzhin ye shes su //
NG0505:55: bag la ma nyams mngon sum du //
NG0505:56: 'gag med ye shes phyogs med gsal //
NG0505:57: rig pa rang gsal rdo rje 'di //
NG0505:59: thams cad mkhyen pa rnams gnyis po //
NG0505:60: dbyer med gcig pa sku gcig ste //
NG0505:61: de las spros na thams cad mkhyen //
NG0505:62: sems can mos pa ji lta ba //
NG0505:63: sangs rgyas sku yang de dang mnyam //
NG0505:64: sangs rgyas 'gro don gang mdzad pa //
NG0505:65: gdul bya de dang mtshungs pa 'byung *//
NG0505:66: chu zla mkha' zla de bzhin no //
NG0505:69: gzhi lam 'bras gsum rang yin pas //
NG0505:71: sems can thams cad rang yin pas //
NG0505:72: byang chub sems dpa' chen po zhes //
NG0505:73: thams cad mkhyen pa'i sangs rgyas yin //
NG0505:74: sems can rang snang ma yin na //
NG0505:75: sangs rgyas gcig gi thugs rjes kyang *//
NG0505:76: gdod nas sems can gcig kyang med //
NG0505:77: thams cad thad ka'i rang snang yin //
NG0505:78: sangs rgyas re la gdul bya re //
NG0505:79: gdul bya re la sangs rgyas re //
NG0505:80: gnyis su med par mnyam pa nyid //
NG0505:81: 'khor ba dong sprugs ma yin pa //
NG0505:82: lhag ma gcig kyang mi 'ong ngo *//
NG0505:83: ji srid sems de yod kyi bar //
NG0505:84: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis ka yod //
NG0505:85: sems kyi gzung 'dzin grol tsam na //
NG0505:86: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis med do //
NG0505:87: gnyis med chos sku kun tu bzang *//
NG0505:88: ngan pa bya ba rdul tsam med //
NG0505:89: bzang po ji bzhin sa dag la //
NG0505:90: kun nas kun tu bzang thob shog / theg chen po yis mngon par rtogs //
NG0505:91: byang chub lam gyi rgyud chen nam mkha' dang mnyam pa las //
NG0505:92: rtsod pa gzhi med du grol bar bstan pa'i le'u ste bco lnga pa'o ///
NG0505:94: snang zhing srid pa'i chos rnams kun //
NG0505:95: sems la ma 'dus chos gzhan med //
NG0505:96: sems nyid kun gyi rtsa ba ste //
NG0505:97: ma rig pa de 'khor ba'i gzhi //
NG0505:98: rig pa'i sems de myang 'das gzhi //
NG0505:99: 'bras bu thams cad skyed par byed //
NG0505:100: kun la khyab pas mkha' lta bu //
NG0505:101: dper na dpag bsam sdong po la //
NG0505:102: yal ga lo 'dab me tog dang *//
NG0505:103: 'bras bu shun pa dri bsung ni //
NG0505:104: lo re zla re zhag re zhing *//
NG0505:106: shing ni slar zhing cher 'phel nas //
NG0505:107: rtsal rdzogs myu gur mi bzlog par //
NG0505:109: byang chub sems kyi chos nyid 'di //
NG0505:110: ma rtogs 'gro ba sems can gyis //
NG0505:111: rang snang rtog pa ji bzhin sgrub //
NG0505:113: rang rang blo dang gang 'tshams pa'i //
NG0505:114: theg pa rim pa sna tshogs pa'i //
NG0505:116: theg pa rnam pa sna tshogs kyang *//
NG0505:117: gang zag 'dod pa tha dad la //
NG0505:118: thabs kyis drang phyir bstan pa las //
NG0505:119: blo chen shes rab ldan pa las //
NG0505:120: de rnams thams cad don gcig par //
NG0505:121: byang chub sems kyi yon tan gyi //
NG0505:122: gnas skabs dus kyi 'bras bu yin //
NG0505:123: sems las ma byung yon tan med //
NG0505:124: thams cad sems kyi cho 'phrul la //
NG0505:125: thad ka'i spyod yul 'bras bu ni //
NG0505:126: phyogs med rgyun du rang sar 'byung *//
NG0505:127: blo chung theg dman phyogs rigs can //
NG0505:128: rang snang med pa gzhan mi rtogs //
NG0505:129: rtogs na theg pa gcig tu 'gyur //
NG0505:130: byang chub sems dpa' chen po'o //
NG0505:131: rang rang 'dod pa'i blo bzhin du //
NG0505:133: 'dzad pa med pa'i byang chub sems //
NG0505:136: stobs dang yon tan cher skyes nas //
NG0505:137: bdag gzhan don gnyis 'grub pa yin //
NG0505:138: rig pa kun mkhyen ye shes su //
NG0505:139: rtsal rdzogs bde ba chen po de //
NG0505:140: phyir mi ldog pa rdo rje'i sku //
NG0505:141: thams cad kun mkhyen kun don grub //
NG0505:142: sangs rgyas sems can don byed kyang *//
NG0505:143: sangs rgyas 'khor bar ldog pa min //
NG0505:144: thugs rje'i 'od kyi nyi ma bzhin //
NG0505:145: sems can snang ngor sangs rgyas byon //
NG0505:146: sangs rgyas gshegs bzhud mi mnga' 'o //
NG0505:147: chos kyi dbyings las ma g.yos par //
NG0505:149: dmus long rang lus mi mthong bzhin //
NG0505:150: ma rig pa la rig pa dka' //
NG0505:151: rigs pa rang byung sgron me 'di //
NG0505:152: mun pa kun sel 'od chen po //
NG0505:153: 'od gsal thams cad mkhyen pa yin //
NG0505:155: theg pa chen po'i mngon par rtogs pa byang chub
NG0505:156: lam gyi rgyud chen nam mkha' dang mnyam pa las
NG0505:157: // byang chub sems kyi 'bras bu dpe dang bcas
NG0505:158: pa bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu drug pa'o // //
NG0505:159: rgya mtsho lta bu'i sde snod kyi //
NG0505:160: snying po yid bzhin nor 'dra ba'i //
NG0505:161: byang chub sems kyi rgyud chen 'di //
NG0505:163: byams pa mgon po khyod la gtad //
NG0505:164: khyod kyis rgyud chen 'gro ba'i don //
NG0505:165: dpag bsam shing chen rgyas bzhin spyod //
NG0505:166: ma 'ongs dus na khyod kyi rigs //
NG0505:167: byang chub sems kyi rgyud 'dzin cing *//
NG0505:169: rgyal bas byin brlabs thugs dbang sras //
NG0505:170: bde chen lam las phyir mi ldog / byang chub dam pa mngon du byed //
NG0505:171: blo gros ldan pa gang zhig gis //
NG0505:172: shes rab spyan gyis rtogs par 'gyur //
NG0505:173: mos sam 'dzin pas tshig re yi //
NG0505:174: don la 'jug pa'i rigs kyi bu //
NG0505:176: legs par zung la yid la chongs //
NG0505:177: nga'i bstan pa gnas kyi bar //
NG0505:179: de nas dga' ldan gnas su 'gro //
NG0505:180: lha dang mi rnams grol bar byed //
NG0505:181: gang zhig nga min nga'i chos //
NG0505:183: bdud kyis byin rlabs glags ltas te //
NG0505:184: byang chub sems rgyud brdzi mi nus //
NG0505:186: 'di nyid bcang ba'i rigs kyi bu //
NG0505:187: sa phyogs gang gnas rgyal ba rnams //
NG0505:188: byin brlobs sems can gang 'brel ba //
NG0505:189: theg chen sa la rim gyis 'gro //
NG0505:190: mi dang mi min rigs tshogs rnams //
NG0505:191: 'di nyid thos pas don ldan te //
NG0505:192: bdud kyis glags skabs mi rnyed cing *//
NG0505:193: ngan song gnas grol thar pa thob //
NG0505:194: gang gis gtsug tu bcangs pa de //
NG0505:195: bla med byang chub phyir mi ring *//
NG0505:196: 'di don rtogs pa'i rigs kyi bu //
NG0505:198: yon tan kun gyi mdzod 'dzin pa'i //
NG0505:199: rgyal bar 'gyur gyis e ma ho //
NG0505:203: ston pa'i gsung la mngon par bstod //
NG0505:204: byang chub sems kyi snying po don //
NG0505:205: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa bla med 'di //
NG0505:206: gang gis bcangs pa'i rigs kyi bu //
NG0505:207: rgyal ba rnams dang dbyer med pa'i //
NG0505:208: yon tan dam pa thob par shog / de nyid mthong ngam thos pas kyang *//
NG0505:209: log rtog bdud kyi tshogs zhi nas //
NG0505:210: mos pas lam la 'khod par shog / de'i ming ngam kha dog gam //
NG0505:211: rus pa dag gis rjes kyi yang *//
NG0505:212: 'gro ba'i 'dod pa tshim par shog / de nyid gnas pa'i sa phyogs su //
NG0505:213: theg pa chen po'i chos spyod cing *//
NG0505:214: sna tshogs dga' ba nyid du shog / 'di spyod myur du sangs rgyas shing *//
NG0505:215: de dang mnyam par gdul bya kun //
NG0505:216: myur du 'khor ba dong sprugs shog / bdag cag rnams kyang de'i dus //
NG0505:218: gnyis su med pa'i dpal du shog / gnyis med 'byor pa dam pa yis //
NG0505:219: mgon po'i zhing khams bde chen du //
NG0505:220: sku gsum sa la 'khod par shog / theg pa
NG0505:221: chen po'am mngon par rtogs pa byang chub lam gyi
NG0505:222: rgyud chen nam mkha' dang mnyam pa las /
NG0505:223: rjes su gtad cing yi rang ba'i le'u ste bcu
NG0505:224: bdun pa'o // // theg pa chen po'i mngon par
NG0505:225: rtog pa byang chub lam gyi rgyud chen nam mkha'
NG0505:226: dang mnyam pa'i rgyud ces bya ba rdzogs so ///
NG0505:227: / o rgyan gyi mkhan po pad+ma 'byung gnas dang *//
NG0505:228: lo tsa ba lcog ro klu'i rgyal mtshan gyis //
NG0505:229: rdo rje gdan gyi gtsug lag khang chen por bsgyur ba'o //
NG0505:230: phyis chos rgyal khri srong lde btsan gyis //
NG0505:231: bsam yas dbu rtse rigs gsum gyi yang stengs su zhus nas //
NG0505:232: u rgyan gyis rang 'gyur du mdzad nas gsungs pa'o //
NG0505:233: sa ma ya rgya rgya rgya ///
NG0505:234: / e ma sangs rgyas bstan pa rin chen gyi //
NG0505:235: sde snod nam mkha' lta ba'i bcud //
NG0505:236: byang chub lam gyi rgyud chen 'di //
NG0505:237: stong gsum gzhan na ma mchis pa'i //
NG0505:238: rgyal ba'i bka' lung bdag la gtad //
NG0505:240: 'dzam gling gzhan du ma spel bar //
NG0505:241: phyi rab lnga brgya'i tha ma la //
NG0505:242: chos rnams tshig tu tha snyad dus //
NG0505:243: rgyud mchog 'di yis phan gdags phyir //
NG0505:244: yi ger bkod nas gter du sbas //
NG0505:245: o rgyan rigs 'dzin thugs kyi sras //
NG0505:246: las can cig dang phrad par shog / gter srungs mkha' 'gro dam can gyis //
NG0505:247: thub par srungs cig sa ma ya /
NG0505:251: bdag 'dra rin chen gling pa la //
NG0505:252: o rgyan pad+ma'i thugs rje yis //
NG0505:253: bka' lung rje'i phyag nas byung *//
NG0505:254: zab mo thugs kyi dgongs gter bton //
NG0505:255: nyams len rgya gar yul du byas //
NG0505:256: sgrub rtags o rgyan yul du bstan //
NG0505:257: 'gro don bod kyi yul du byas //
NG0505:258: dga' ldan gnas su dgongs pa rdzogs //
NG0505:259: bde ba can du don gnyis rdzogs //
NG0505:260: gter chos zab mo rgya mtsho nas //
NG0505:261: khyad mchog byang chub lam rgyud @#//
NG0505:263: o rgyan thugs kyi dgongs gter nas //
NG0505:264: lcag po 'brug la gdan drangs nas //
NG0505:265: bla ma'i bka' bzhin shog ser nas //
NG0505:266: zhal bshus bka' shog dag la ni //
NG0505:267: me pho khyi'i lo la mnan //
NG0505:268: 'di dus ngo mtshar can gyi rtags //
NG0505:269: bsam gyis mi khyab brjod las 'das //
NG0505:270: yin kyang da ki'i bka' rgyas btab //
NG0505:271: gter nas gdan drangs zhal bshus pa'i //
NG0505:272: yi ge 'di nyid mthong thos dran //
NG0505:273: yid la mos byed dpe mtshon nas //
NG0505:274: mkha' mnyam 'gro kun ma lus pa //
NG0505:275: rgyud 'di dgongs pa lon nas su //
NG0505:276: myur du sangs rgyas thob par shog / mam g+ha la wa tu /
